structure.unit: PUBLIC LAWS IN FORCE -- COURT RULES

law.history: Repealed 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 62, sec. 135, effective June 19, 1976. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 18, sec. 2, effective February 25, 1952.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Bench and bar to receive proposed rules -- Procedure for consideration of suggestions and amendments -- Time for distributing rules.
